---
// src/pages/index.astro
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import aboutMeDay from '../assets/images/arturo-lopez-day.png';
import aboutMeNight from '../assets/images/arturo-lopez-night.png';
import beautifulCancunLarge from '../assets/images/beautiful-cancun-large.webp';
import beautifulCancunHalf from '../assets/images/beautiful-cancun-half.webp';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import SectionColumn from '../components/SectionColumn.astro';
import SectionRow from '../components/SectionRow.astro';
import SectionTitle from '../components/SectionTitle.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Arturo López Gómez - Líder Técnico">
    <Header title="Arturo López" />
    <main>
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
            <!-- Imagen de fondo con overlay sutil -->
            <picture>
                <!-- Imagen para pantallas grandes -->
                <source srcset={beautifulCancunLarge.src} media="(min-width: 1024px)" type="image/webp" />
                <!-- Imagen para pantallas móviles -->
                <source srcset={beautifulCancunHalf.src} media="(max-width: 1023px)" type="image/webp" />
                <Image 
                    src={beautifulCancunLarge}
                    alt="Beautiful Cancún" 
                    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center"
                    style="filter: brightness(0.75);" 
                    loading="eager"
                />
            </picture>

            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/50 z-0"></div>

            <!-- Contenido -->
            <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center space-y-8">
                
                <!-- Badge de disponibilidad -->
                <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-1.5 bg-green-100 text-green-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium shadow-sm animate-bounce-subtle">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-2 animate-pulse-slow"></div>
                    Arquitectura • Microservicios • Mentoría • Observabilidad • Side Projects
                </div>

                <!-- Título principal -->
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold  leading-tight text-white animate-pop">
                    Construyo productos escalables
                    <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 animate-gradient-text">
                        y comparto lo que aprendo
                    </span>
                </h1>

                <!-- Descripción -->
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
                    Líder Técnico en Revenatium (2019–actual) • Java, Spring Boot, Next.js • Arquitectura de microservicios, observabilidad y prácticas de ingeniería
                </p>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
                    Bitácora de aprendizajes y side projects (laboratorio personal).
                </p>

                <!-- Botones -->
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
                    <a href="#contact" 
                        class="px-8 py-4 rounded-xl bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold text-lg shadow-md hover:bg-blue-700 hover:shadow-lg transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                        Notas técnicas
                    </a>
                    <a href="#projects" 
                        class="px-8 py-4 rounded-xl border border-white/40 text-white hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white transition-colors duration-300 font-semibold text-lg">
                        Ver proyectos personales
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Flecha hacia abajo -->
            <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce" aria-hidden="true" onclick="document.getElementById('about').scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });" style="cursor: pointer;">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white/70" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </section>


		
        <SectionColumn id="about" title="Sobre Mí" accent="bg-white  outline-dashed outline-stone-100 outline-offset-0">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                Soy Ingeniero en Sistemas y Líder Técnico enfocado en diseñar y escalar productos web con Java, Spring Boot y arquitectura de microservicios. Me interesan los fundamentos: diseño modular, resiliencia, contratos claros, observabilidad y delivery predecible.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                En mi día a día en Revenatium lidero iniciativas de arquitectura y evolución de plataforma. Fuera de horario, mantengo un “laboratorio personal” de side projects donde exploro ideas, pruebo patrones y documento aprendizajes. Me motiva compartir prácticas que funcionen en equipos reales.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3" aria-label="Tecnologías usadas">
                <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-java-100 text-java-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Java</span>
                <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-spring-100 text-spring-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Spring Boot</span>
                <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-micro-100 text-micro-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Microservicios</span>
                <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-nextjs-100 text-nextjs-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Next.js</span>
                <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-devops-100 text-devops-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">DevOps</span>
            </div>
            <div class="relative" slot="content">
                <div class="w-full h-96 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-purple-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                    <picture>
                        <!-- Imagen para pantallas grandes -->
                        <source srcset={aboutMeDay.src} media="(min-width: 1024px)" type="image/png" />
                        <!-- Imagen para pantallas móviles -->
                        <source srcset={aboutMeNight.src} media="(max-width: 1023px)" type="image/png" />
                        <Image 
                            src={aboutMeDay}
                            alt="Sobre mí - Arturo López Gómez" 
                            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center rounded-2xl -m-5"
                            loading="eager"
                        />
                    </picture>
                </div>
                <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center animate-pulse-slow cursor-pointer animate-pop-scale-and-rotate-15 transition-all duration-100" onclick="window.location.href='/about-me'" title="Conoce más sobre mí">
                    <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">15+</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </SectionColumn>

        <SectionTitle id="experience" title="Laboratorio de ideas" accent="bg-gray-100 outline-dashed outline-stone-100 outline-offset-0">
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Selección de casos que documentan decisiones de diseño, patrones aplicados y aprendizajes prácticos. Algunos fueron desarrollados en entornos empresariales; otros pertenecen a mi laboratorio personal de side projects.
            </p>
            <!-- Más experiencias -->
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8" slot="content">
                <!-- Project SpringBoot+Course -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Curso SpringBoot + Kotlin</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">En curso, es un repositorio de aprendizaje práctico sobre desarrollo de aplicaciones con Spring Boot y Kotlin. Aquí nos enfocaremos en contenido de calidad, orientado a resolver problemas reales.</p>
                    <a href="https://github.com/lgzarturo/springboot-course/wiki" target="_blank" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Ver proyecto</a>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4" aria-label="Tecnologías usadas">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-java-100 text-java-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Java</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-spring-100 text-spring-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Spring Boot</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-micro-100 text-micro-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Microservicios</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Project Blog -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Blog Personal</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">A lo largo de mi carrera, he compartido mis conocimientos y experiencias en un blog personal, donde publico artículos sobre desarrollo de software, mejores prácticas y tutoriales.</p>
                    <a href="https://www.arthurolg.com/" target="_blank" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Ver proyecto</a>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4" aria-label="Tecnologías usadas">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-java-100 text-java-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Astro</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-spring-100 text-spring-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Markdown</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-micro-100 text-micro-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Webp</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Project Bootzen -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Bootzen</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Micro Framework con PHP para el desarrollo de aplicaciones web. El objetivo es simplificar el proceso de creación de aplicaciones web al proporcionar una estructura básica y herramientas útiles.</p>
                    <a href="https://github.com/lgzarturo/bootzen" target="_blank" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Ver proyecto</a>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4" aria-label="Tecnologías usadas">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-php-100 text-php-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">PHP</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-spring-100 text-spring-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">HTML</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-micro-100 text-micro-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">CSS</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Project Loyalty -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Programa de Lealtad</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Migración completa a arquitectura de microservicios con Spring Boot, logrando +25% en suscriptores y mejoras en ventas.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2" aria-label="Tecnologías usadas">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-java-100 text-java-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Java</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-spring-100 text-spring-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Spring Boot</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-micro-100 text-micro-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Microservicios</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Project ATS -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">ATS StarTalent.mx</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Rediseño completo del sistema de reclutamiento con Grails y Spring, crecimiento del +60% en clientes corporativos.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2" aria-label="Tecnologías usadas">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-grails-100 text-grails-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Grails</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-spring-100 text-spring-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Spring</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-nextjs-100 text-nextjs-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Next.js</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Project Booking Engine -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 group">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-purple-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Motor de Tarifas</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Sistema de carga masiva por layout que redujo tiempos operativos en un 40% y eliminó errores manuales, permitiendo una mayor eficiencia.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2" aria-label="Tecnologías usadas">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-java-100 text-java-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Java</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-spring-100 text-spring-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Spring Boot</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-postgresql-100 text-postgresql-800 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">PostgreSQL</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </SectionTitle>

        <SectionTitle id="skills" title="Colaboraciones y comunidad" accent="bg-white outline-dashed outline-stone-100 outline-offset-0">
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                No estoy en búsqueda activa de empleo. Si surge una conversación interesante de tecnología y producto, siempre es bienvenida. Estos son mis intereses actuales:
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6" slot="content">
                <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-300 group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Liderazgo Técnico</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Mentoring, Arquitectura, Equipos Ágiles</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-300 group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Desarrollo Backend</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Java, Spring Boot, Microservicios, APIs REST</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-300 group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Desarrollo Frontend</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Next.js, React, TypeScript, TailwindCSS</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-6 rounded-2xl hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-300 group">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">DevOps & Cloud</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Docker, AWS, CI/CD, Kubernetes</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </SectionTitle>
        
        <SectionTitle id="projects" title="Experiencia Profesional" accent="bg-gray-100">
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 text-center mb-12">15+ años construyendo productos y plataformas</p>
            <!-- Timeline visual -->
            <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl" slot="content">
                <!-- Línea vertical central -->
                <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-0 h-full w-1 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-400 via-gray-300 to-gray-400 -translate-x-1/2 z-0"></div>

                <div class="flex flex-col gap-20 relative z-10">
                    <!-- Nodo más reciente: Líder Técnico -->
                    <div id="lider-tecnico" class="timeline-node group relative flex flex-col items-center md:items-start">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6 ml-41 md:ml-0">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 border-4 border-blue-300 rounded-full shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center animate-pulse-slow z-10"></div>
                            <span class="text-blue-700 font-bold text-lg">2019 - Actualidad</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-2xl border-2 border-blue-600 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 w-full">
                            <h4 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-blue-900 mb-1">Líder Técnico</h4>
                            <p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold mb-2">Revenatium</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                                Enfocado en la transformación digital del motor de reservaciones hoteleras, migrando sistemas legados 
                                a arquitecturas modernas con microservicios. Dirijo equipos multidisciplinarios y mentoreo 
                                desarrolladores en buenas prácticas y tecnologías emergentes.
                            </p>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2" aria-label="Tecnologías usadas">
                                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-java-100 text-java-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Java</span>
                                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-spring-100 text-spring-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Spring Boot</span>
                                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-micro-100 text-micro-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Microservicios</span>
                                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-aws-100 text-aws-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">AWS</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Nodo: Arquitecto de Software -->
                    <div id="arquitecto-software" class="timeline-node group relative flex flex-col items-center md:items-start">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6 ml-25 md:ml-0">
                            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-400 border-4 border-blue-200 rounded-full shadow-md z-10"></div>
                            <span class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-base">2018 - 2019</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-blue-200 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 w-full">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Arquitecto de Software</h4>
                            <p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold mb-2">StarChoice / StarTalent.mx</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                                Rediseñé completamente el sistema ATS con tecnologías modernas, escalando la plataforma 
                                de PyME a referente en soluciones de reclutamiento para hotelería. Implementé prácticas 
                                DevOps y arquitecturas escalables.
                            </p>
